<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center;"><a href="/wiki/File:Candide1759.jpg" class="image" title="Frontispiece of the 1759 edition published by Sirène in Paris"><img alt="Frontispiece of the 1759 edition published by Sirène in Paris" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4c/Candide1759.jpg/200px-Candide1759.jpg" width="200" height="400" border="0" /></a><br />
